'''布赖恩·马克·布莱克韦尔'''（{{lang-en|Brian Mark Blackwell}}，{{bd|1986年}}），英国男性，2004年7月25日18岁时在[[英格兰|英格兰]][[利物浦|利物浦]]附近的家中用刻刀和羊角锤将自己的父母杀害。<ref name="guardian2005_carter">{{Citation|first=Helen|last=Carter|title=Fast lane fantasies of a model pupil who bludgeoned his parents to death|date=29 June 2005|journal=The Guardian|place=UK|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2005/jun/30/ukcrime.helencarter|access-date=6 May 2016|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918083832/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2005/jun/30/ukcrime.helencarter|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 早年生活 ==
布赖恩·马克·布莱克韦尔于1986年出生于西兰开夏郡，母亲杰奎琳·布莱克韦尔（Jacqueline Blackwell）曾是古董商，父亲悉尼·布莱克韦尔（Sydney Blackwell）则是退休会计师。<ref name="telegraph2005">{{Citation|first=Nigel|last=Bunyan|title=Psychological time bomb that turned teenage son into frenzied killer|journal=The Telegraph|place=UK|date=30 June 2005|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1493035/Psychological-time-bomb-that-turned-teenage-son-into-frenzied-killer.html|access-date=7 May 2016|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712202019/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1493035/Psychological-time-bomb-that-turned-teenage-son-into-frenzied-killer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="guardian2005_staff">{{Citation|last=Staff and agencies|title=Teenager admits killing parents|date=29 June 2005|journal=The Guardian|place=UK|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2005/jun/29/ukcrime|access-date=7 May 2016|archive-date=2018-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708133147/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2005/jun/29/ukcrime|dead-url=no}}</ref>2004年7月以前，布莱克威尔一直与父母一起住在默西塞德郡梅林——英格兰利物浦北郊的一个富裕村庄。<ref name="telegraph2007">{{Citation|last=Sally Peck and agencies|title=Son who killed parents must pay back £37,000|journal=The Telegraph|place=UK|date=13 February 2007|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1542474/Son-who-killed-parents-must-pay-back-37000.html|access-date=6 May 2016|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712202022/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1542474/Son-who-killed-parents-must-pay-back-37000.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的父母对他十分溺爱<ref name="times2005_jenkins">{{Citation|last=Jenkins|first=Russell|title=Narcissus schoolboy who killed his parents is cleared of murder|date=30 June 2005|journal=The Times|place=London, UK|issn=0140-0460|quote=Mr Justice Royce accepted that Brian Blackwell, 19... had acute narcissistic personality disorder. He ordered that a double murder charge be dropped, allowing Blackwell to admit manslaughter on the grounds of diminished responsibility}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title='I long to be a little boy again' - the son who killed his parents|date=30 June 2005|journal=The Times|place=London, UK|issn=0140-0460|quote=The cossetted only child who beat his parents to death...}}</ref>。他曾是当地俱乐部18岁以下网球冠军，<ref>{{Citation|title=Murdered pair 'stabbed not shot'|date=8 September 2004|journal=BBC News|place=Merseyside, England, UK|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/3636576.stm|access-date=6 May 2016|archive-date=2018-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708110539/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/3636576.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>也曾被利物浦学院授予奖学金，被誉为“模范学生”，并计划于2004年秋天开始在[[諾丁漢大學|诺丁汉大学]]学习医学。<ref name="bbc2005_son" />

他会经常讲一些谎话，例如把自己的学业成绩往好了说，这些谎话无关痛痒，但两个月内他的谎言越来越过分，最终导致他在2004年7月杀害父母。<ref name="guardian2005_carter"/>他为了凑够钱参加夏末的[[法国网球公开赛|法网]]公开赛，以父亲的名义申请了13张信用卡，<ref name="bbc2005_son">{{Citation|title=Son gets life for killing parents|journal=BBC News|place=Merseyside, England, UK|date=29 June 2005|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4633339.stm|access-date=6 May 2016|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222045444/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4633339.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>并声称自己是职业网球选手。他在申请表上写道，他将能够以每年45,000英镑的工资偿还贷款。他当时的女友也相信他是一名职业网球选手，有耐克的赞助，和足球运动员[[史提芬·謝拉特|史蒂芬·杰拉德]]住同一个建筑群，有6万英镑的奔驰和45万英镑的公寓。<ref name="bbc2005_killer">{{Citation|title=Killer Blackwell's fantasy life|date=29 June 2005|journal=BBC News|place=Merseyside, England, UK|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4634401.stm|access-date=6 May 2016|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220061709/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4634401.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>他用父母准备给他上大学的储蓄券，给女友买了昂贵的礼物，“雇佣”她做经理，给她开了一张39000英镑的支票。<ref name="telegraph2005" />当他母亲发现他对银行撒的谎后，她马上和银行方面取得联系。 

== 杀人 ==
2004年7月25日，布莱克韦尔用[[羊角錘|羊角锤]]和刻刀砸死、刺死了自己的父母。<ref name="guardian2005_carter"/>至于作案动机，他在2005年受审时说，父母对他的奢侈消费表示担忧，想阻止他与女友前往美国，他气从中来，非常愤怒。<ref name="telegraph2005" /><ref name="times2005_jenkins">{{Citation|last=Jenkins|first=Russell|title=Narcissus schoolboy who killed his parents is cleared of murder|date=30 June 2005|journal=The Times|place=London, UK|issn=0140-0460|quote=Mr Justice Royce accepted that Brian Blackwell, 19... had acute narcissistic personality disorder. He ordered that a double murder charge be dropped, allowing Blackwell to admit manslaughter on the grounds of diminished responsibility}}</ref><ref name="guardian2005_staff"/>

第二天，他的女友还不知道布莱克韦尔犯下的罪行，仍然和他按原定计划去美国度假。<ref name="telegraph2005" />八月中旬回到利物浦后，布莱克韦尔在他女朋友家住了两个星期，谎称父母去西班牙度假了，他进不了自己家。<ref name="guardian2005_carter"/><ref name="smh">{{Citation|last=The Telegraph, London|title=Narcissist son bludgeoned parents to death|date=30 June 2005|journal=The Sydney Morning Herald|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/narcissist-son-bludgeoned-parents-to-death/2005/06/30/1119724732433.html|access-date=6 May 2016|archive-date=2016-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221143757/http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/narcissist-son-bludgeoned-parents-to-death/2005/06/30/1119724732433.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

== 调查和起诉 ==
2004年9月5日，布莱克韦尔父母遇害六周后，邻居打电话报告房屋内散发出强烈的异味，警方才终于发现了两人的腐尸。<ref name="guardian2005_staff"/>布莱克韦尔于次日被捕<ref name="bbc2004">{{Citation|title=Son held after couple shot dead|date=6 September 2004|journal=BBC News|place=Merseyside, England, UK|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/3630540.stm|access-date=7 May 2016|archive-date=2018-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902221000/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/3630540.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并被控两项谋杀罪。<ref name="times2005_jenkins">{{Citation|last=Jenkins|first=Russell|title=Narcissus schoolboy who killed his parents is cleared of murder|date=30 June 2005|journal=The Times|place=London, UK|issn=0140-0460|quote=Mr Justice Royce accepted that Brian Blackwell, 19... had acute narcissistic personality disorder. He ordered that a double murder charge be dropped, allowing Blackwell to admit manslaughter on the grounds of diminished responsibility}}</ref>他一开始矢口否认这些指控，并在审判前被保释候审。<ref>{{Citation|title=Son sent for trial|journal=The Times|place=London, UK|date=18 January 2005|issn=0140-0460|quote=Brian Blackwell, 18, a former public schoolboy, denied murdering his father, Brian, 72, and mother, Jacqueline, 61, last July... Liverpool Crown Court remanded him in custody for trial in May.}}</ref> 

布莱克韦尔声称当时自己正在度假，对父母的死亡一无所知。经过两天的询问，布莱克韦尔才改变了说辞。他对罪行供认不讳，但仍表示他拿着一把羊角锤在墙上挂画，父亲过来要打他，他出于自卫才将父母杀害。调查人员此前获悉，布莱克韦尔的父亲是坐着被锤中后脑勺，与布莱克威尔的说法相冲突。

专家诊断出他患有[[自戀型人格疾患|自恋型人格障碍]]。他承认了较轻的过失杀人罪后，双重谋杀罪指控被撤销。<ref name="bbc2005_son"/>布莱克韦尔于2005年6月29日被判处[[無期徒刑|无期徒刑]]。<ref name="guardian2005_staff"/>

